      "source_repo": "radekd91/emoca",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "Official repository accompanying a CVPR 2022 paper EMOCA: Emotion Driven Monocular Face Capture And Animation. EMOCA takes a single image of a face as input and produces a 3D reconstruction. EMOCA sets the new standard on reconstructing highly emotional images in-the-wild"
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "source-snippet",
